Command: note (arg)
         Add lines into your personal notebook. Available to players
         above level 10.

Examples: 
        note (or note read) 
                Displays the contents of your notebook.

        note Remember to e-mail janina.frostell@nalle.com about dinner!
                Adds a line to the notebook.

        note erase 1
                Erases the line marked as 1 from the notebook.

        note reset (or note clear)
                Clears all entries from the notebook.

